Package com.poli.human_resources_managment_server.model

Class Historic

java.lang.Object
com.poli.human_resources_managment_server.model.Historic
public class Historic extends Object
Represents a historical record of an employee's career events in the system. This class holds information about a historical event, including the ID of the record, the date of retirement, job ID, employee ID, and department ID.
